name: A7
description:
This is the seventh piece in a series which will be "assembled." It is considered an "element." Collectors must acquire all seven elements (A1-A7) by a specified date to receive the fully assembled piece via airdrop. In order to receive the completed piece, the full set of seven elements must be burned by sending to waambatburn.tez. Collectors may choose to hold the individual elements or assemble the full piece, but there will only be one window of time in which to do so.

Follow @waambat on twitter for specific burn instructions.
Burn window will run from the January 26th, 5pm PST - February 2nd, 5pm PST
